msgid "Parameters for the dashboard backend of the customer company config item overview of the agent interface . \"Limit\" is the number of entries shown by default. \"Group\" is used to restrict the access to the plugin (e. g. Group: admin;group1;group2;). \"Default\" determines if the plugin is enabled by default or if the user needs to enable it manually. \"CacheTTLLocal\" is the cache time in minutes for the plugin."
msgstr ""
"פרמטרים עבור לוח המחוונים האחורי של פריט התצורה של חברת הלקוח בסקירת ממשק "
